**Author:** GregorSec

It uses the Standard Galactic Alphabet (SGA) as a substitution cipher. SGA is used in Minecrafts enchantment table symbols/the Commander Keen video game. Each english letter is mapped to a unique unicode symbol. 

I go to [https://lingojam.com/standardgalacticalphabet](https://lingojam.com/standardgalacticalphabet) and input the SGA string. The site shows: `Qregorcec{to0_inf1nity_4nd_b3y0nd}`.
